OL,3,CWoman found guilty of sexual offence
OL,4,Cagainst 18-year-old man on beach
OL,6,FA 44-year-old woman in Jersey has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of a sexual offence
OL,8,Fagainst an 18-year-old male on
OL,9,FLiberation Day.
OL,11,FClaire Louise Fowell was arrested on
OL,12,Fthe evening of 9 May 2025, after she
OL,13,Fwas alleged to have sexually touched
OL,14,Fthe man without his consent.
OL,16,FHe was reportedly spending time on the
OL,17,Fbeach with his friends, before the
OL,18,Fwoman touched his inner thigh and then
OL,19,Fattempted to pull down his shorts.
