OL,3,CWoman found guilty of sexual offence
OL,4,Cagainst 18-year-old man on beach
OL,6,FFowell pled not guilty to the charge
OL,7,Fon 30 October 2025, at Jersey's
OL,8,FMagistrate Court.
OL,10,FShe was found guilty on 13 March 2026,
OL,11,Ffollowing a two-day trial at the same
OL,12,Flocation.
OL,14,FShe will appear for sentencing on 24
OL,15,FApril 2026.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
