OL,3,CWoman found guilty of sexual offence
OL,4,Cagainst 18-year-old man on beach
OL,6,FFollowing the trial, Detective
OL,7,FInspector Christina Maclennan said:
OL,8,F"Sexual offending in any form is
OL,9,Fcompletely unacceptable and today's
OL,10,Fconviction reflects our commitment to
OL,11,Fensuring that those who commit such
OL,12,Foffences will be held to account."
